tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE diversity_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(50),
    impact_score INT,
    cultural_changes TEXT,
    report_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE initiative_details (
    initiative_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    initiative_type VARCHAR(50),
    initiative_start_date DATE,
    initiative_end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE employee_diversity_feedback (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_id INT,
  feedback TEXT,
  rating INT,
  submitted_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE impact_of_diversity_initiatives (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    initiative_name VARCHAR(255),
    impact_score INT,
    report_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE employee_diversity_data (
    employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    department_name VARCHAR(255),
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    ethnicity VARCHAR(50),
    hire_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE survey_responses (
    response_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    employee_id INT,
    survey_question VARCHAR(255),
    response_score INT,
    response_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE company_culture_metrics (
    metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_name VARCHAR(255),
    metric_value FLOAT,
    metric_date DATE
)
